BobUI 6.0.0 is a new major version release of BobUI. It is not binary compatible with
earlier BobUI releases.

The goal has been to retain as much source compatibility with BobUI 5.15 as
possible, but some changes were inevitable to make BobUI a better framework.

To make it easier to port to BobUI 6.0, we have created a porting guide to
summarize those changes and provide guidance to handle them. In the guide, you
can find links to articles about changes that may affect your application and
help you transition from BobUI 5.15 to BobUI 6.0:

https://doc.bobui.io/bobui-6/portingguide.html

For more details refer to the online documentation of BobUI 6.0:

https://doc.bobui.io/bobui-6/index.html

